name: Happy Mix
description: A lovely happy mix for your hamster!

name: Rainy Day Mix
description: Is is a very rainy day? Let your hamster indulge in my rainy day mix for a wonderful, productive afternoon!

name: Lovely Mix
description: The Lovely Mix is exactly what the name implies -- Lovely! Perfect for smaller, more temperate hamsters, to keep them energized throughout the day.

name: Prada Mix
description: Prada Mix is exclusively for hamsters that are into the top tiers of fashion.

name: Cute Mix
description: Do you want your hamster to be the cutest little thing? This mix is for you!

name: Silly Mix
description: Only for silly hamsters that spend ALL of their day goofing around. Not for serious hamsters.

name: Prada 2 Mix
description: Prada 2 Mix, the second rendition of the Prada Mix, offers not much more -- but for a lot more. Only for the hardcore fashionista hamsters.

name: Vegan Mix
description: Hamsters with upset stomachs are quickly cured with this wonderful vegan mix.

name: Rock Mix
description: That's right, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson presents his own special mix just for your hamster.
